Endpoint Method Description <code>/health</code> GET Basic health check <code>/livez</code> GET Liveness check (process alive) <code>/readyz</code> GET Readiness check (can serve traffic) <p>Health response: <pre><code>{
  "status": "healthy",
  "version": "1.0.0"
}
</code></pre></p> <p>Readiness response: <pre><code>{
  "ready": true,
  "checks": {
    "database": true,
    "cache": true,
    "provider": true
  }
}
</code></pre></p>
